videos.description: Malik Newman gets Kansas going quickly with an alley-oop to Udoka Azubuike.
videos.headline: Azubuike starts off with alley-oop

videos.description: Malik Newman drives and dishes to Devonte' Graham who knocks down a quick 3-pointer for the Jayhawks.
videos.headline: Graham hits catch-and-shoot 3

videos.description: Devonte' Graham hits two 3-pointers and a fadeaway jumper to put the Jayhawks up 26-21.
videos.headline: Graham scores 8 straight for KU

videos.description: Udoka Azubuike rolls off the screen and rocks the rim with a one-handed jam for Kansas.
videos.headline: Azubuike slips screen for jam

videos.description: Devonte' Graham gets a home bounce on a 3-pointer to put the Jayhawks up 60-54.
videos.headline: Graham gets the bounce on 3

videos.description: Udoka Azubuike launches off the screen and leaps for an and-1 dunk to put Kansas up 6.
videos.headline: Azubuike draws foul on dunk

videos.description: Kouat Noi races along the baseline and slams it home for the Horned Frogs.
videos.headline: Noi launches for TCU dunk
